      messages.
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
      Linux &lt;a href="/status/compiler_status.html"&gt;Compiler Status&lt;/a&gt; added.
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;
      Boost source code now lives in a publicly accessible Concurrent Versions System
      (CVS) repository.
    &lt;/li&gt;
